    <h2 class="act-title">The Repetition and Pattern Game</h2>
    <p class="act-desc">Two parts. First: how your child handles sustained repetition — and whether a format change visibly re-engages them. Second: what ceiling of rule complexity they reach when given complete freedom to construct a pattern.</p>
